# 1. Ignore all build directories
**/target/
**/node_modules/

# 2. Ignore common binary extensions (Windows/Generic)
*.exe
*.pdb
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# 3. Handle extensionless binaries (Linux/macOS)
# This ignores every file by default...
*
# ...BUT keeps the directories so we can see inside them
!*/
# ...AND "un-ignores" your actual source code and config files
!*.rs
!*.toml
!*.md
!*.lock
!.gitignore
!*.png
!*.jpg